Caster Level(s): Wizard / Sorcerer 5Innate Level: 5School: Conjuration ( Teleportation )Descriptor(s): Component(s): Verbal, SomanticRange: PersonalArea of Effect / Target: CasterDuration: Permament until readSave: NoneSpell Resistance: NoThe caster inscribes a magical rune of  power on the targeted item, usually his spell book which activates upon being read. Once read it the chosen item immediately teleports back to the wizard and disappears. If the spell dimensional anchor is cast on the spell book, the caster is dead or on another plane the spell has no effect.